# Servly UI Agent Notes

This workspace contains independently publishable Servly UI packages.

## Rules

- Do not modify `/Users/eddiesosera/Documents/Dev/Servly/noPrompt-portal` from this workspace unless the user explicitly asks for portal integration.
- Keep package APIs typed and documented before exporting them.
- Keep package behavior covered by Vitest or React Testing Library tests when behavior changes.
- Do not add a shared abstraction until at least two packages need it.
- Prefer package-local README updates when changing public props, exports, or install instructions.
- Treat Tailwind as a default design-system preset, not as the only supported design system.
- Preserve consumer styling hooks such as slot-level `classNames`, `styles`, and adapter injection when changing UI internals.

## Commands

Run from the workspace root:

```bash
npm install
npm run lint
npm run typecheck
npm test
npm run build
npm run pack:dry-run
```

Run from `packages/number-input`:

```bash
npm run typecheck
npm run lint
npm test
npm run build
npm run pack:dry-run
```
